| logical_plan  | Sort: x.channel ASC NULLS LAST, x.id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=100                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |   Projection: x.channel, x.id, sum(x.sales) AS sales, sum(x.returns) AS returns, sum(x.profit) AS profit                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
